   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>In the consulate of our lord emperor Maximianus Augustus for the 6th time and Constantius who is among the gods. Aurelius Ar... son of Ammonios from the village of A. . . of the Oxyrhynchite nome, to [. . .] Ammon, veteran, and however you style yourself, greeting. I acknowledge that I have received from you as a loan five artabas of barley . . .
</ab>
